msgid ""
"Bayes factor interpretation: BF ≥ 10 (strong evidence for H−), 3 ≤ BF < 10 "
"(moderate evidence for H−), 0.33 ≤ BF < 3 (inconclusive), 0.10 ≤ BF < 0.33 "
"(moderate evidence for H+), BF < 0.10 (strong evidence for H+)."
msgstr ""
"Interpretasi faktor Bayes: BF ≥ 10 (bukti kuat untuk H–), 3 ≤ BF < 10 (bukti "
"moderat untuk H–), 0.33 ≤ BF < 3 (inkonklusif), 0.10 ≤ BF < 0.33 (bukti "
"moderat untuk H+), BF < 0.10 (bukti kuat untuk H+)."

msgid "Procedure"
msgstr "Prosedur"

msgid ""
"<div style='line-height: 1.2;'>\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0;'>The <b>main objective</b> of this Bayesian "
"sampling procedure is to evaluate the quality of a lot by determining if the "
"proportion of defects is lower than the <b>Rejectable Quality Level (RQL)</"
"b>, which is currently set at <b>%1$.2f%%</b>.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 4px 0;'>Two primary statistical hypotheses are "
"formulated about the lot proportion defective (&theta;):</p>\n"
"    <ul style='margin: 0 0 8px 20px;'>\n"
"      <li>The (null) hypothesis of intolerable quality H<sub>+</sub>: "
"&theta; &ge; %1$.2f%% (user-defined)</li>\n"
"      <li>The (alternative) hypothesis of tolerable quality H<sub>-</sub>: "
"&theta; < %1$.2f%% (user-defined)</li>\n"
"    </ul>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0;'>Additionally, users have the option to "
"perform a <b>Three-Hypothesis Test</b>, which partitions the quality levels "
"into 'Good' (&le; AQL), 'Middle' (AQL < &theta; &le; RQL), and 'Bad' (> RQL) "
"regions.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0;'>The <b>Acceptable Quality Level (AQL)</b> "
"is currently set at <b>%2$.2f%%</b>. This value represents the\n"
"    quality level aimed for acceptance with high probability. These quality "
"constraints can be adjusted in the Planning phase to reflect specific "
"requirements.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 6px 0;'><b>Stages</b></p>\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 6px 0;'><b>1. Planning:</b> Determine a minimum "
"sample size such that the sample provides sufficient evidence (a target "
"Bayes factor) to achieve the specified sampling objectives.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0;'><b>2. Inference:</b> Evaluate observed data to "
"update the prior belief into\n"
"    a posterior distribution. In this section, <b>n</b> denotes the sample "
"size, <b>d</b> the observed number of defects in the sample, and <b>N</b> "
"the lot size.</p></div>"
msgstr ""
"<div style='line-height: 1.2;'>\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0;'><b>Objektif utama</b> dari prosedur "
"pensampelan Bayes ini adalah mengevaluasi kualitas dari lot dengan "
"menentukan jika proporsi dari cacat lebih rendah dari <b>Tingkat Kualitas "
"Dapat Ditolak (RQL)</b>, yang saat ini diatur di <b>%1$.2f%%</b>.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 4px 0;'>Dua hipotesis statistikal primer "
"dirumuskan tentang defektif proporsi lot (&theta;):</p>\n"
"    <ul style='margin: 0 0 8px 20px;'>\n"
"      <li>Hipotesis (null) dari kualitas tidak dapat ditoleransi H<sub>+</"
"sub>: &theta; &ge; %1$.2f%% (ditentukan pengguna)</li>\n"
"      <li>Hipotesis (alternatif) dari kualitas dapat ditoleransi H <sub>-</"
"sub>: &theta; < %1$.2f%% (ditentukan pengguna)</li>\n"
"    </ul>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0;'>Secara tambahan, pengguna memiliki opsi "
"untuk melakukan <b>Pengujian Tiga-Hipotesis</b>, yang mempartisi tingkat "
"kualitas menjadi wilayah 'Baik' (&le; AQL), 'Tengah' (AQL < &theta; &le; RQL)"
", dan 'Buruk' (> RQL).</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0;'><b>Tingkat Kualitas Dapat Diterima (AQL)</"
"b> saat ini diatur di <b>%2$.2f%%</b>. Nilai ini merepresentasikan\n"
"    tingkat kualitas bertujuan untuk penerimaan dengan probabilitas tinggi. "
"Kendala kualitas ini dapat disesuaikan di fase Perencanaan untuk "
"mencerminkan persyaratan spesifik.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 6px 0;'><b>Tahapan</b></p>\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0 0 6px 0;'><b>1. Perencanaan:</b> Tentukan ukuran "
"sampel minimum sedemikian sampel menyediakan bukti cukup (faktor Bayes "
"target) untuk mencapai objektif pensampelan tertentu.</p>\n"
"\n"
"    <p style='margin: 0;'><b>2. Inferensi:</b> Evaluasikan data terobservasi "
"untuk memperbarui keyakinan priori menjadi\n"
"    distribusi posterior. Di bagian ini, <b>n</b> menandakan ukuran sampel, "
"<b>d</b> jumlah cacat terobservasi di sampel, dan <b>N</b> ukuran lot.</p></"
"div>"

msgid ""
"Lower limit for proportion non-conforming items needs to be smaller than the "
"upper limit."
msgstr ""
"Batas bawah untuk item non-konform proporsi perlu lebih kecil dari batas "
"atas."

msgid ""
"Step size for proportion non-conforming items needs to be smaller than the "
"difference between the upper and lower limits."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran langkah untuk item non-konform proporsi perlu lebih kecil dari "
"perbedaan antara batas atas dan bawah."

msgid ""
"Step size of 0 is allowed only if the lower and upper limits of proportion "
"non-conforming items are identical."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran langkah 0 diizinkan hanya jika batas bawah dan atas item non-konform "
"proporsi identik."

msgid ""
"For hypergeometric distribution, N * proportion non-conforming should all be "
"integer values.\n"
"\n"
"Check the values of N and proportion non-conforming."
msgstr ""
"Untuk distribusi hipergeometris, N * non-konform proporsi harus semua nilai "
"integer.\n"
"\n"
"Periksa nilai N dan non-konform proporsi."

msgid "Sample size (n) cannot be larger than the lot size (N)."
msgstr "Ukuran sampel (n) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran lot (N)."

msgid "Acceptance number (c) cannot be larger than the sample size (n)."
msgstr "Angka penerimaan (c) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran sampel (n)."

msgid "Rejection number (r) cannot be larger than the sample size (n)."
msgstr "Angka penolakan (r) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran sampel (n)."

msgid "Rejection number (r) has to be larger than the acceptance number (c)."
msgstr "Angka penolakan (r) harus lebih besar dari angka penerimaan (c)."

msgid ""
"Cumulative sample size (n1+n2+...) cannot be larger than the lot size (N)."
msgstr ""
"Ukuran sampel kumulatif (n1+n2+...) tidak dapat lebih besar dari ukuran lot "
"(N)."

msgid ""
"Final rejection number (r) needs to be 1 more than the final acceptance "
"number (c)."
msgstr ""
"Angka penolakan akhir (r) harus 1 lebih dari angka penerimaan akhir (c)."

msgid ""
"Rejection number (r) for every stage has to be larger than the corresponding "
"acceptance number (c)."
msgstr ""
"Angka penolakan (r) untuk setiap tahap harus lebih besar dari angka "
"penerimaan yang sesuai (c)."

msgid ""
"For all stages except the last stage, rejection numbers (r) have to be at at "
"least 2 greater than the acceptance numbers (c).\n"
"\n"
"                                   Else, subsequent stages become redundant."
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua tahap kecuali tahap terakhir, angka penolakan (r) harus "
"setidaknya 2 lebih dari angka penerimaan (c).\n"
"\n"
"                                   Tidak, tahap subsekuen menjadi rendundan."

msgid ""
"Acceptance numbers (c) are cumulative, so they need to be in a non-"
"decreasing sequence."
msgstr ""
"Angka penerimaan (c) kumulatif, jadi mereka harus dalam sekuens non-"
"penurunan."

msgid ""
"Rejection numbers (r) are cumulative, so they need to be in a non-decreasing "
"sequence."
msgstr ""
"Angka penolakan (r) kumulatif, jadi mereka harus dalam sekuens non-penurunan."

msgid "No valid values found in the plan. Check the inputs."
msgstr "Tidak ada nilai valid ditemukan di rencana. Periksa masukan."

msgid ""
"AQL (Acceptable Quality Level) value should be lower than RQL (Rejectable "
"Quality Level) value."
msgstr ""
"Nilai AQL (Tingkat Kualitas Diterima) harus bawah dari nilai RQL (Tingkat "
"Kualitas Ditolak)."

msgid "1 - α (Producer's risk) has to be greater than β (consumer's risk)."
msgstr "1 - α (Risiko produsen) harus lebih dari β (risiko konsumen)."

msgid "Current plan <b>CAN %s</b> meet the specified risk point(s)."
msgstr "Rencana saat ini <b>DAPAT %s</b> memenuhi titik risiko tertentu."

msgid "Proportion Non-conforming"
msgstr "Non-konform Proporsi"

msgid "Required P(accept)"
msgstr "Diperlukan P(terima)"

msgid "Actual P(accept)"
msgstr "Aktual P(terima)"

msgid ""
"Probability of acceptance (%1$.3f) at AQL (%2$.3f) is <b>lower</b> than the "
"required probability of acceptance (%3$.3f) at AQL."
msgstr ""
"Probabilitas penerimaan (%1$.3f) di AQL (%2$.3f) <b>lebih rendah</b> dari "
"probabilitas penerimaan diperlukan (%3$.3f) di AQL."

msgid ""
"Probability of acceptance (%1$.3f) at RQL (%2$.3f) is <b>higher</b> than the "
"required probability of acceptance (%3$.3f) at RQL."
msgstr ""
"Probabilitas penerimaan (%1$.3f) di RQL (%2$.3f) <b>lebih tinggi</b> dari "
"probabilitas penerimaan diperlukan (%3$.3f) di RQL."

msgid "Acceptance Probabilities"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penerimaan"

msgid "Prop. Non-conforming"
msgstr "Non-konform Prop."

msgid "P(accept)"
msgstr "P(terima)"

msgid "OC (Operating Characteristics) Curve"
msgstr "Kurva OC (Karakteristik Operasi)"

msgid "Probability of Acceptance"
msgstr "Probabilitas Penerimaan"

